RULES:
1. Analyze the DOM structure carefully to find elements matching the description
2. Prefer semantic selectors: data-testid > id > name > class > tag+attribute > tag
3. For click actions: look for:
   - Button elements: <button>, <input type="submit">, <input type="button">
   - Links: <a>
   - Elements with role="button"
